    "department": "👷‍♂️ Fixa",
    "description": "ABOUT THE COMPANY\n\nFixa is building the HR and financial infrastructure for Africa’s informal and blue-collar workforce. Our platform supports businesses in construction, manufacturing, agriculture, and other labor-intensive sectors with powerful tools for workforce management, payroll, payments, and financial services.\n\n\nABOUT THE ROLE\n\nWe are looking for a Head of Finance who will lead Fixa’s financial strategy, systems, and team as the company scales across markets. This role combines strong technical finance expertise with hands-on operational leadership in a high-growth fintech environment.\n\n\n\n\nCORE RESPONSIBILITIES\n\n - Lead budgeting, forecasting, cash flow management, and financial modeling\n\n - Build and manage a high-performing finance team\n\n - Partner closely with Product and Engineering to design and improve internal financial systems and reconciliation workflows\n\n - Oversee financial reporting, investor updates, and board materials\n\n - Drive unit economics, clarity, and support strategic decision-making\n\n - Ensure regulatory compliance across multi-market operations\n\n\nQUALIFICATIONS\n\n - 8–9 years total experience; qualified accountant (ACCA, CPA, CA or equivalent)\n\n - 2–5 years at a rapidly scaling fintech (e.g., companies like Paystack, Impeza or similar growth-stage African fintechs)\n\n - Currently a Finance Manager or Senior Finance Manager, ready for VP/Head of Finance progression\n\n - Proven experience building finance teams and implementing scalable systems\n\n - Strong cross-functional experience with product and tech teams\n\n - Comfortable operating in Pan-African, multi-currency environments\n\n\nSUCCESS INDICATORS\n\n - Clean, timely, and reliable monthly reporting with zero surprises\n\n - Clear visibility into cash runway, burn, and capital needs at all times\n\n - Strong financial controls with minimal reconciliation gaps or audit issues\n\n - Unit economics are clearly defined, tracked, and used in leadership decisions\n\n - Finance systems that scale seamlessly as transaction volume and markets grow\n\n - A high-performing finance team that operates independently and proactively\n\n - Investors and board members express strong confidence in financial clarity and discipline",
    "employment_type": "FullTime",
